\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 相对C300，C400无论在读取还是写入性能上提升都很明显，特别是在写入速度方面，对于组建高端平台的用户是个不错的选择，高达415MB/s的读取速度，相对那些传统硬盘，游戏加载速度快了好几倍，即使那些入门级的SSD也只能望尘莫及。另外SSD超低的延迟，使得惊醒文件的读取和写入时，很难感到有延迟。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','images/201308/thumb_img/4526_thumb_G_1377568608212.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4526_G_1377568608508.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4526_G_1377568608658.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1377568608','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1377568608','4','','0','0','0','');
