ding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">●<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">测试小结：相对C300性能提升很明显</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 通过SATA 6Gbps和SATA 3Gbps的数据，我们可以看出SATA 3Gbps接口远远不能满足C400的速度要求，强烈建议用户不要连接SATA 3Gbps接口。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 相对C300，C400无论在读取还是写入性能上提升都很明显，特别是在写入速度方面，对于组建高端平台的用户是个不错的选择，高达415MB/s的读取速度，相对那些传统硬盘，游戏加载速度快了好几倍，即使那些入门级的SSD也只能望尘莫及。另外SSD超低的延迟，使得惊醒文件的读取和写入时，很难感到有延迟。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>','images/201308/thumb_img/4527_thumb_G_1377569226511.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4527_G_1377569226243.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4527_G_1377569226610.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1377569226','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1377569226','4','','0','0','0','');
